HEADWORD: Batrachomyomachy
<hw>Bat`ra*cho*my*om"a*chy</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>batrachomyomachi`a</grk>; <grk>ba`trachos</grk> frog +
<grk>my^s</grk> mouse + <grk>ma`chh</grk> battle.]</ety> <def>The battle
